WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.360
Wives. Do not do this to your husbands.

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:04.520
I was at the thrift store yesterday with my husband,

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:05.960
and we were just shopping around,

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:06.920
looking at all the cool stuff.

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.840
This lady comes up to me and she goes,

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:09.840
what is this called?

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:11.460
Holding up a spatula?

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:12.760
And I said, oh,

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:13.920
well, that's a spatula.

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:14.600
And she goes,

00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:15.800
see, I told him.

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:17.880
I told him it was a spatula,

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:19.320
not a pancake flipper.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.480
And you could tell that her husband was sheepish,

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:23.480
was walking away,

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:25.780
did not wanna be part of this conversation at all.

00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:27.780
And I thought to myself, you know,

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:29.840
this doesn't prove him wrong.

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.200
This just proves that you're disrespectful

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:34.760
not only in public to completely random strangers,

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:36.040
but you're also disrespectful,

00:00:36.040 --> 00:00:38.060
most likely in your home as well.

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:41.000
Her attitude towards him was not a reflection on him

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.960
and what he thought this thing was called.

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:44.440
It was a reflection on her

00:00:44.440 --> 00:00:47.680
and how contentious and brash and loud she was being.

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:48.760
I guarantee you

00:00:48.760 --> 00:00:51.240
her husband felt extremely disrespected

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:53.280
and extremely emasculated.

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:55.440
So do not do this to your husband's.

00:00:55.440 --> 00:00:56.797
It does not come off well.
